name: Robot Greeting Card Set
description:
Printed on 100% recycled paper, these awesome, cool hip robot greeting cards are perfect for all occasions! Each card is blank on the inside you can figure out what to say to match the exterior.

These cards are based off of my original illustrations posted at my blog www.mattspangler.com and each has its own story.

Heart bot: He likes Tuesdays as much as sandwiches, meet heart-bot. This guy is just happy to see anyone.

Howdy bot: Just waving, saying hello this guy is just saying hello!


Flower bot: Revealing robots have a little more than just 1's and 0's, this guy is sentimental, cute and nice to send when someone may be having a bad day. 

Cards are 4"x6"s and come with plain white envelopes.
